Usage: {{Tl|Heatmap|scope=year/month/last|year=YYYY|month=MonthName|mode=releases}}

Examples:
* {{Heatmap|scope=last}} - rolling last 365 days
* {{Heatmap|scope=year|year=2026}} - calendar year
* {{Heatmap|scope=month|year=2026|month=March}} - single month
* {{Heatmap|scope=year|year=2026|mode=releases}} - explicit metric mode

Renders a GitHub-style heatmap of documented obby releases per day.
